l.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/CHDM/111%2c%e7%b0%a1%2c2069%2c20221107%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"CHDM,111,簡,2069,20221107,1","JYEAR":"111","JCASE":"簡","JNO":"2069","JDATE":"20221107","JTITLE":"妨害公務"}